sources.sass\\base\\_typography.sass:
p
    font-size: var(--font-size)
    line-height: var(--ratio)

h1
    font-size: var(--h1)
    line-height: calc(var(--h1) * var(--ratio))

h2
    font-size: var(--h2)
    line-height: calc(var(--h2) * var(--ratio))

h3
    font-size: var(--h3)
    line-height: calc(var(--h3) * var(--ratio))

h4
    font-size: var(--h4)
    line-height: calc(var(--h4) * var(--ratio))

.semi-bold
    font-weight: var(--body-w-500)

.bold
    font-weight: var(--body-w-700)

.uppercase
    text-transform: uppercase

.blocknote
    padding-left: var(--spacer)
    border-left: var(--border) solid var(--clr-secondary-200)

.letter-spacing
    letter-spacing: var(--gap)
sources.sass\\base\\_body.sass:
html, body
    height: 100%

body
    font-family: var(--body-font), var(--body-type)
    font-size: var(--font-size)
    color: var(--clr-primary-300)
    background: var(--clr-background-100)
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased
    -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%

*
    box-sizing: border-box
sources.sass\\base\\_links.sass:
a, ul, li
    margin: 0
    padding: 0
    cursor: pointer

a
    font-size: var(--font-size)
    text-decoration: none
    decoration: none
    outline: 0
    line-height: 0
    opacity: 1
    transitio: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out
    color: var(--clr-secondary-200)

    &:hover,
    &:focus
        opacity: 0.8
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out

ul
    list-style: none
sources.sass\\layout\\_general.sass:
.container
    width: calc(100% - var(--margin)*2)
    max-width: var(--xl)
    margin: 0 auto
sources.sass\\layout\\_grid.sass:
$column: map-get($grid, column)

.row
    display: flex
    flex-wrap: wrap

[class^=col-]
    flex-basis: 100%

@for $i from 1 through $column
    .col-#{$i}
        padding: var(--gap)
        flex: 0 0 100%
        +mq(lg)
            flex: 0 0 (100% / ($column / $i))
    .col-offset-#{$i}
        margin-left: 0
        +mq(lg)
            margin-left: 100% / ($column / $i)
